node.text:
Two events often left out of American History curriculum.  
We've teamed up with the @chicagobulls to create a virtual program for two high schools in both Chicago and Tulsa to learn about these events.

node.title: The Chicago Race Riot of 1919 & the 1921 Tulsa Race Massacre.
